      *              * Se Delt                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DELT"
                     move  "X"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-tes
                     go to acc-cat-scr-999.
       acc-cat-scr-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-num                to   w-tes-cat-scr (1)      .
       acc-cat-scr-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
