      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      03                   to   w-let-arc-zcs-tip      .
           move      w-tes-cat-scr (1)    to   w-let-arc-zcs-cod      .
           perform   let-arc-zcs-000      thru let-arc-zcs-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
