      *                      * malizzato al valore 1                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-tip-pro (1)    to   w-wrk-tip-pro          .
           if        w-prs-epz-rgf-val
                    (w-wrk-tip-pro)       not  = zero
                     move  w-prs-epz-rgf-val
                          (w-wrk-tip-pro) to   w-tes-epz-rgf (1)
           else      move  1              to   w-tes-epz-rgf (1)      .
       cnt-tdo-nok-510.
