      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Descrizione per i listini                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Che non sia a spaces                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-daa-lst (1)    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-lst-800.
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-des-lst (1)      .
       cnt-tdo-nok-lst-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita post-normalizzazioni                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-lst-999.
       cnt-tdo-nok-lst-850.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
