      *                  * Forzature                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Si/no gestione a listino                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      0                    to   w-tes-snx-lst (1)      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Si/no descrizione per listino           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      0                    to   w-tes-daa-lst (1)      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Elementi da esporre per i listini       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      all "X"              to   w-tes-epz-lst (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-lst-999.
       cnt-tdo-nok-lst-900.
