           move      spaces               to   w-tes-prm-ubi (1, 2)   .
       cnt-tdo-nok-mau-520.
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-prm-ubi (1, 3)   .
       cnt-tdo-nok-mau-530.
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-prm-ubi (1, 4)   .
       cnt-tdo-nok-mau-800.
